          %p{style:"color: white; font-size: 11px"} The Nike + Fuelband allows you to live life as a sport as you recieve "fuelpoints" for the activity that you do throughout the day. Run, walk, play ball, and live life as you keep track of your activity in a new and innovative way!
      .item
        = link_to (image_tag("reviews_promo.jpg", size: "700x319")), '/posts?category=reviews'
        .carousel-caption
          %h4=link_to "Product Reviews", "/posts?category=reviews"
          %p{style:"color: white; font-size: 11px"} Read reviews for all different types of athletic and running shoes, running watches, and other running accessories!
      / .item store
